Class DoubleWrapper

java.lang.Object
  org.jlinalg.RingElement
      org.jlinalg.FieldElement
          org.jlinalg.DoubleWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<IRingElement>, IRingElement
public class DoubleWrapper
extends FieldElement
implements IRingElement

This class wraps a double value and performs all FieldElement operations on that double. Fast but not without rounding errors.

Author:
Andreas Keilhauer, Georg Thimm
